    ZonedDateTime zdtHongKong = instant.atZone( zHongKong ) ;

…and…

    ZoneId zLosAngeles = ZoneId.of( &quot;America/Los_Angeles&quot; ) ;
    ZonedDateTime zdtLosAngeles = instant.atZone( zLosAngeles ) ;

All three objects refer to the same moment, the same point on the timeline. 

To produce strings, call `toString`.

